    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, I feel I’m unable to do what others can do."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "As I look all around me, they all seem more useful to You."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "But I see, dear Lord, I‘m here for Your need,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "To build up Your church today!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "And You gave these gifts that I may be trained,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, perfect me, I pray!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "verse",
      "number": "2"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, I’m ready and willing to be perfected by You,"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Through the saints all around me, to build Your Body too!"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "type": "chorus"
    },
    {
      "lines": [
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "In the church I’m perfected by the saints with the life supply."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "I am growing and building, as I learn to minister Christ!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "“Till we all arrive,” yes, this is our goal!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Every member builds today!"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, I give myself, Your Body to build."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "segments": [
            {
              "chord": "",
              "text": "Lord, for this now I pray!"
            }
          ]
        }
